{"tid":911330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女與魚性交懷上異形　家人不相信醫學真相","createTime":"2018-11-22T00:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T01:53:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ae776478db88b52c326f44baefe49fd55e60d8de","tid":911330,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:14:24.000Z","msg":"菲律賓一名17歲少女貝希娜(Kimberly Robles Besinal)，自去年6月開始，肚子開始異常凸起，家人都相信她跟魚性交後，懷上異形，卻不相信醫學真相。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，貝希娜說，她的肚子從去年6月開始隆起，而且出現疼痛症狀。家人認為貝希娜在外面亂搞男人懷孕，於是帶她去照超音波，但照出來的結果更讓家人崩潰，因為照片顯示出貝希娜的子宮內懷有一條「魚」。貝希娜表示，家人開始相信當地傳說，女生沒穿內褲到海裡游泳，就會被海中異形趁虛而入交媾，射爆陰戶幽洞，進而讓女子懷上小異形。<br />\n報導指出，當地有著一個奇怪習俗與傳說，那就是女生月經來潮時，最好到海上待個5天，直到經期結束。而女生如果在月經來潮期間，沒穿內褲下水游泳，就容易被海中異形勾引而交媾，最後懷上小異形。<br />\n不過1年過去了，貝希娜沒有生下小異形，於是再到醫院做進一步檢查。醫師法南德茲(Massachusette Fernandez)表示，貝希娜不是懷上魚類異形，這是卵巢囊腫，而貝希娜也因為這個囊腫，讓她的體重從40公斤增加到50公斤。貝希娜說，因為囊腫，讓她感覺到疼痛且呼吸困難，現在她正籌錢，準備動手術摘除。<br />\n貝希娜的父親羅伯斯(Pablo Robles)坦承，原本家人都相信她與男生或魚魚偷情並懷孕，不相信貝希娜堅稱的「沒有男友」，但現在真相大白，終於願意相信她。不過貝希娜說，她的阿嬤和堂姊仍然相信她與魚兒亂搞。（施旖婕／綜合外電報島）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_62ed8d088885031843060690f600f747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_62ed8d088885031843060690f600f747.jpg&h=372d8fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_de43601c8077c563dbb4e2ddae04700a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_de43601c8077c563dbb4e2ddae04700a.jpg&h=e8591508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181122/640_cbf35bfcb47eb837b75d2d05da26bc6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181122%2F640_cbf35bfcb47eb837b75d2d05da26bc6f.jpg&h=83b61acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181122/1470907/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181122%2F1470907%2F&d=6Zvx9h4%2B8YMvnTGnfB%2FsIdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b4e9e49e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181122%2F1470907%2F&h=92c77e0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181122/1470907/</a>"},{"pid":"0f26d15ed2a47cb188ed49000a849f9beeeecd9c","tid":911330,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:20:38.000Z","msg":"相對論幾多年後會被推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478e5dc0df365e63f0ea9657e37c6ee62d5a4938","tid":911330,"uid":2133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"尾二咁似賓賓穎"},{"pid":"196c7311fb01d8685bf4a9dc4afce831de1e8608","tid":911330,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:29:41.000Z","msg":"貝希娜堅稱「沒有男友」<br />\n關咩事<br />\n邏輯問題..."},{"pid":"48aa13a143e8cba5c57438bee157187931b34473","tid":911330,"uid":37933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"深潛者？"},{"pid":"e97a003e49de92d3e08100abfbf4cceaf59027df","tid":911330,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"478e5dc0df365e63f0ea9657e37c6ee62d5a4938","tid":911330,"uid":2133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"尾二咁似賓賓穎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"賓穎似賓賓有咩出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc98e337023f7cee074b4f37187a8b6276d3c4e","tid":911330,"uid":103294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"普羅米修斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6905ddf481e4a3d21372106834f7868cf672c62","tid":911330,"uid":17628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"